highlights.text: “Every Breath You Take” by The Police is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 63 spots at #113.
“MORE” by j-hope is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #22.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #4.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 283 weeks straight.
